This is an in-depth introduction to R for any new beginner. Don't worry its pretty easy!!

Please make sure to install R before you start: https://cran.r-project.org/bin/windows/base/

Please make sure to install one the IDEs
R.console : https://cran.r-project.org/bin/windows/base/
OR
RStudio: https://posit.co/download/rstudio-desktop/
